Package cnuphys.tinyMS.common

Class Summary
ByteSwap Methods used for byte swapping.
Common Common static methods used by clients and the server.
Environment This utility class holds environmental information such as the home directory, current working directory, host name, etc.
ReaderThread This thread uses a IMessenger object to read messages, and then places the messages on the IMessenger's inbound queue.
WriterThread This thread uses a IMessenger object to write (transmit) messages that it dequeues from the Imessenger's outbound queue.
